      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……顔を洗うのにここまで時間が掛かるとは\nやれやれ、酷い目にあったな",
      "startTime": 6.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、やっと綺麗になりましたか\n随分と時間が掛かりましたね～？",
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "頬に描かれた巨大プリンの絵を消すのに\n特に苦労したよ、まったく……",
      "startTime": 17.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえばなんですけど\nさっき、写真をリズノワのグループに送ったんです",
      "startTime": 23.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　写真って……なんの写真だ？",
      "startTime": 27.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん、こころに大敗した\n{user}さんの写真です！",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、さすがは我らが星見プロのマネージャー！",
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事を管理するだけでなく、時に笑いという\n癒しを提供してくれる……素晴らしいです！",
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7033.3333333,
          "startTime": 53.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……リズノワのみんなはどんな反応をしてたんだ？",
      "startTime": 50.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "まず莉央さんなんですけど、めずらしくお腹を抱えて\nぷるぷるしてましたね～",
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "その動画を撮ってる葵さんもこれまためずらしく\n笑いを堪えてました～",
      "startTime": 65.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "後は愛ちゃんですけど、「笑い過ぎて楽屋の椅子から\n転げ落ちたんだけど！」って報告がきましたね～",
      "startTime": 72.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ笑ってくれたなら何よりだよ……\n……こほん",
      "startTime": 80.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？\nわざとらしい咳払いなんかしちゃって",
      "startTime": 83.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "実はな、明日のリズノワの予定を調整して\n仕事の合間に空き時間を二時間だけ作ったんだ",
      "startTime": 90.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "え！",
      "startTime": 93.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "これなら四人で初詣に行けると思ってな",
      "startTime": 94.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんな風に時間が空いたら\nみんな別々の予定を入れちゃうんじゃあ……",
      "startTime": 101.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それなら心配ないよ。こころがみんなと初詣に\n行きたがってるって伝えたからな",
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったです～……\nって、ちょっとー！　なんで言っちゃうんですかー！",
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なんせ急な話だからな\n気持ちを素直に伝えた方が話は早いだろ？",
      "startTime": 120.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "それはまぁ、そうですけど……",
      "startTime": 124.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "くぅ～……{user}さんに\n好き放題に心を弄ばれてますぅ～……！",
      "startTime": 132.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺はさっき、こころに好き放題に顔面を\n弄ばれたんだけどな……",
      "startTime": 139.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、ありがとうございます\nすっごく嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 145.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったよ\n四人でゆっくり楽しんでくれ",
      "startTime": 149.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか～\n{user}さんも一緒ですよ！",
      "startTime": 154.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも、四人で行った方が\n楽しめるんじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 159.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です、{user}さんは\nいてもいなくても、こころ達は自然体ですから！",
      "startTime": 163.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5933.333333400014,
          "startTime": 167.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それは褒めてないよな……？",
      "startTime": 167.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、葵さん、愛ちゃんも同意してます！\nこれなら問題ないですよね？",
      "startTime": 173.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "第一ですね、大人気……いや、超人気\nアイドルグループのリズノワが初詣に行くんですよ？",
      "startTime": 180.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "パニックになった時の生贄……\nいえ、守ってくれる人がいないと心細いです～",
      "startTime": 187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "今、はっきり生贄って言ったよな……？　でも、確かに\n四人で行くのは大変か……分かった、俺も行くよ",
      "startTime": 196.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、それじゃあ明日は五人で初詣といきましょ～！",
      "startTime": 200.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 207.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18165.729204799987,
          "startTime": 219.0657292048
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
