      "text": "ふむふむ、なかなかいい感じですね！\n着物姿で四人並ぶと壮観ですね～",
      "startTime": 228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "よ～し、この調子でどんどん撮っちゃいましょう！\nポージングと表情の指定はこころにお任せあれ！",
      "startTime": 235.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
