      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "次は莉央さんがセクシーポーズ、葵さんが満面の笑顔\n愛ちゃんは両腕をムキッとさせましょう！",
      "startTime": 244.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_03-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "こころですか？　こころは舌をぺろっと出した\n可愛さ満点の天使スマイルを……",
      "startTime": 252.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
